      "text": "When we capture the structure of the story in a causal loop diagram we open up opportunities:\n\n- The process of mapping engages us in the story. \n- It allows us to understand the story better and to be able to craft better questions about it. \n- It enables us to see what might have been unintentionally or intentionally left out. \n- It enables us to rewrite our stories with increased clarity and without any \"fluff\"\n- It gives us a framework for creating many new stories - as the story related is just one possible behavior pattern which could emerge from the structure.\n"
